Dialogue: 0,00:06:04.980,00:06:10.720,辉英,,0,0,0,,which we will talk later. The simplest type of boundary condition is u0 which
Dialogue: 0,00:06:10.720,00:06:15.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,is u at the left hand side of the domain has to equal to a specific value at the
